sentence:
The policy of my Government with regard to foreign affairs can be summarized as follows:

(1) Adherence to the United Nations Charter and to international laws and conventions;

(2) Establishment of our relations with those countries with which we exchange diplomatic recognition and relations in accordance with the principles of sovereignty and territorial integrity, non-interference in the internal affairs of others, non-aggression, equality and mutual interest, and peaceful coexistence, as embodied in United Nations resolutions.
